text.tspan: ColaHacks is an hackathon hosted at the
University of South Carolina in Columbia, SC.
Students from USC and other universities will
come together to bring their ideas to life in the
form of web, mobile, hardware, and any
development. Students will have 12 hours to
learn, build, and have fun in a fast-paced yet
compete to show judges why their project
makes a difference for the chance to win
